      "value": "<p>At 11th level, your technique allows you to critically hit anyone, regardless of their defenses.</p><p> When you would score a critical hit on a creature, but they have a trait, jutsu, or feature that block critical hits, you may spend an additional 5 cursed energy to ignore that trait, jutsu, or feature.</p><p> When you spend Cursed Energy to do this, you ignore resistance.</p><p></p>",
